read it on the AO3 at https://ift.tt/2Dpo0K5

by crispybacon

Sequel to “Promise of Tomorrow”

Takes place immediately following the end of the first, right after Steve and Tony marry. Follow the family’s journey as they maneuver through obstacles, exes, illnesses, teen drama and bullies…all within the first year.

Also includes daddy-Bucky flashbacks. Also also mind the tags.

summary: Have You Kissed Your Favourite Genius Today?  Let’s Stony like it’s 2012! This was a sketch I drew a while after Civil War...
caption:
Have You Kissed Your Favourite Genius Today?

Let’s Stony like it’s 2012!

This was a sketch I drew a while after Civil War (let’s call it therapy) but I have faced the fact that I’m never going to finish it. Not aside from cleaning it up some and slapping on some flat colours. So yeah. Here we are. I hope you enjoy some old-fashioned Stony!

by Littledarkshine

Ruby Bell lives in a world where the government has decided that everything super-human related should be erased from the planet. She never knew anything else until she found herself in a place she didn’t belong, in a time she didn’t belong. But she learned to accept her fate.
But just when she thought she found a place she belonged she had to run. her friend became her worst nightmare and it was her own fault. She ran for 67 years before her past caught up to her, but not in a way she would have expected.
